item.title: CVE-2020-7861|2024-08-04T09:41:01.876Z -- koino -- aquanplayer
item.description: AnySupport (Remote support solution) before 2019.3.21.0 allows directory traversing because of swprintf function to copy file from a management PC to a client PC. This can be lead to arbitrary file execution.
